293cb957-f00c-4a65-9a09-0ffbf5177d4c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use the same color as the center block, and starting at each corner of the center block, make a diagonal line that continues to each corner.
293cb957-f00c-4a65-9a09-0ffbf5177d4c.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same as the input grid.
293cb957-f00c-4a65-9a09-0ffbf5177d4c.see_description: In the input, you should see...a solid colored grid with the center block a different color.
